          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/494.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Once </strong>the onion is soft, add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(2 tbsp)</span> sugar, Henderson's relish, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(4 tbsp)</span> water and the remaining red wine vinegar to the pan</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reduce</strong> the heat to very low and simmer gently for another 10-15 min or until sticky and sweet</p>\r\n<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, put the ciabattas in the oven for 5 min or until crusty and hot</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/494.-step-5-x200.jpg",
