            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Slice</strong> the cheese into 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">(4)</span> slices</p>\r\n<p><strong>Slice</strong> the steak</p>\r\n<p><strong>Wash</strong> half <span class=\"text-danger\">(all)</span> the salad (use any remainder for lunch tomorrow) in cold water and pat dry with tea towel</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> hot, remove the ciabattas from the oven and slice in half&nbsp;</p>",
